SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section A, Line 6
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: APPLICATIONS FOR MEMBERSHIP ARE ACCEPTED DURING THE ANNUAL MEMBERSHIP RECRUITMENT PERIOD. MEMBERS MUST RESIDE IN THE HUNTINGTON BEACH UNION HIGH SCHOOL DISTRICT AREA AND CAN APPLY TO ONLY ONE CHAPTER. MEMBERS MAY VOTE AND HOLD OFFICE. MEMBERS SHALL PAY ANNUAL DUES, FULFILL SERVICE HOURS AND ATTENDANCE OBLIGATIONS AS SPECIFIED IN THE BY-LAWS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section B, Line 11b
